channel.title: Project pluto, experience out of this world
channel.description:
[center][b]Project Pluto[/b][/center] What is project pluto? A soon to be server strictly based on having a good economy and community with active pking. Just an all out fun to play server made for everyone. This server will NOT have customs such as retarded shit like dildos. It will have a dedicated founder, I plan to stick to this project and complete it. This server will get hosted, I will pay fees for VPS/Advertisement etc. The development team will receive a percentage of the donations, by development team I mean people who were in from the start. Not admin/moderators.
Devolopment team thread: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,544879.0.html
[center][b]Media[/b][/center] [img]http://i.imgur.com/TP6Kl.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/SciUl.png[/img]

I hope you have a ton of goals for this server rather than just downloading Iquality, changing the name, and hosting. Good luck regardless
[/quote]
Why would you assume I changed the name? It doesn’t even have the name in the 2 pictures I have posted, smh at ignorant dicks like yourself.[/quote]

I didn’t assume you dumb fucking inbred, I sure as hell would hope that you change the name though. Instead of being that incompetent, and purely downloading IQuality without even 1% of credits towards yourself. I was not being a dick but I sure as hell can be you dumb ass. I was simply making a suggestion and wishing you luck. Smh at dumbfucks like yourself.

Edit: I do not retract my initial comment above, although I apologize for the vulgarity displayed. Long day.
